(129, 'Inglourious Basterds', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//bPnPsyo09tLRnTOb7AlsBsgnbhP.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//7sfbEnaARXDDhKm0CZ7D7uc2sbo.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a group of Jewish-American soldiers known as \"The Basterds\" are chosen specifically to spread fear throughout the Third Reich by scalping and brutally killing Nazis. The Basterds, lead by Lt. Aldo Raine soon cross paths with a French-Jewish teenage girl who runs a movie theater in Paris which is targeted by the soldiers.', 44, '2009-08-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/KnrRy6kSFF0', 8, 16432, 153, 'United States', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Brad Pitt, Christoph Waltz, Mélanie Laurent, Diane Kruger, Michael Fassbender, Daniel Brühl, Eli Roth, Til Schweiger, B.J. Novak, August Diehl, Mike Myers, Omar Doom, Sylvester Groth, Denis Menochet, Richard Sammel, Jacky Ido, Martin Wuttke, Julie Dreyfus, Samm Levine, Gedeon Burkhard, Rod Taylor, Christian Berkel, Léa Seydoux, Eva Löbau\r\n', 'War. Action. Comedy. II World War. Nazism. Revenge '),
(130, 'Children of Paradise', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//59kBgtfbhh1dalgjGvFhDL98jN.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//yiy9stl1jjVhW44ypkWMFDT8Ix3.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'fr', 'Filmed during the German occupation, this French milestone centers around the theatrical life of a beautiful courtesan and the four men who love her. Voted the “Best French Film in History” by the French Film Academy in 1990.', 9, '1945-03-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3tdXMgY42H0', 8, 229, 191, 'France', 'Marcel Carné', 'Jacques Prévert', 'Jean-Louis Barrault, Pierre Brasseur, Pierre Renoir, Arletty, Marcel Herrand, María Casares, Louis Salou, Gérard Blain\r\n', 'Romance. Drama | Stage Play. 19th Century. Romantic Drama. French Poetic Realism '),
(131, 'Star Wars', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//zqkmTXzjkAgXmEWLRsY4UpTWCeo.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//6FfCtAuVAW8XJjZ7eWeLibRLWTw.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'Princess Leia is captured and held hostage by the evil Imperial forces in their effort to take over the galactic Empire. Venturesome Luke Skywalker and dashing captain Han Solo team together with the loveable robot duo R2-D2 and C-3PO to rescue the beautiful princess and restore peace and justice in the Empire.', 82, '1977-05-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/1g3_CFmnU7k', 8, 15238, 121, 'United States', 'George Lucas', 'George Lucas', 'Mark Hamill, Harrison Ford, Carrie Fisher, Alec Guinness, Peter Cushing, David Prowse, Peter Mayhew, Anthony Daniels, Kenny Baker, Phil Brown, Shelagh Fraser, Garrick Hagon, Denis Lawson, Alex McCrindle, Richard LeParmentier, Drewe Henley, Jack Purvis, Don Henderson, William Hootkins, Malcolm Tierney\r\n', 'Sci-Fi. Adventure. Space Adventure. Cult Movie. Star Wars '),
(132, 'La Dolce Vita', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//zPbu0CFnAT2kYfbGWjgZBTajmzi.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//5Zq9pAs3Y9TrFHxO0nEbq3QVTtj.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'it', 'Journalist and man-about-town Marcello struggles to find his place in the world, torn between the allure of Rome\'s elite social scene and the stifling domesticity offered by his girlfriend, all the while searching for a way to become a serious writer.', 18, '1960-02-05', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/1BeWEPXWDX4', 8, 1183, 176, 'Italy', 'Federico Fellini', 'Federico Fellini, Tullio Pinelli, Ennio Flaiano, Brunello Rondi', 'Marcello Mastroianni, Anita Ekberg, Anouk Aimée, Yvonne Furneaux, Alain Cuny, Nadia Gray, Annibale Ninchi, Magali Noël, Lex Barker, Jacques Sernas, Adriano Celentano, Ida Galli\r\n', 'Drama. Comedy. Journalism. Film In Film '),
(133, 'Memento', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//q2CtXYjp9IlnfBcPktNkBPsuAEO.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//yuNs09hvpHVU1cBTCAk9zxsL2oW.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'Leonard Shelby is tracking down the man who raped and murdered his wife. The difficulty of locating his wife\'s killer, however, is compounded by the fact that he suffers from a rare, untreatable form of short-term memory loss. Although he can recall details of life before his accident, Leonard cannot remember what happened fifteen minutes ago, where he\'s going, or why.', 24, '2000-10-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/HDWylEQSwFo', 8, 10716, 113, 'United States', 'Christopher Nolan', 'Christopher Nolan (Story: Jonathan Nolan)', 'Guy Pearce, Carrie-Anne Moss, Joe Pantoliano, Mark Boone Junior, Stephen Tobolowsky, Harriet Sansom Harris, Jorja Fox\r\n', 'Thriller. Mystery. Crime. Revenge. Neo-noir. Cult Movie. Independent Film (US) '),
(135, 'All About Eve', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//9LkOiz3fPTEhZbXr5IvdFbm01cj.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//6numIZH6uR3NlJgY9m7nGH0jhs.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'From the moment she glimpses her idol at the stage door, Eve Harrington is determined to take the reins of power away from the great actress Margo Channing. Eve maneuvers her way into Margo\'s Broadway role, becomes a sensation and even causes turmoil in the lives of Margo\'s director boyfriend, her playwright and his wife. Only the cynical drama critic sees through Eve, admiring her audacity and perfect pattern of deceit.', 11, '1950-10-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/LSntQerk8cQ', 8, 1005, 139, 'United States', 'Joseph L. Mankiewicz', 'Joseph L. Mankiewicz', 'Bette Davis, Anne Baxter, George Sanders, Celeste Holm, Gary Merrill, Hugh Marlowe, Gregory Ratoff, Barbara Bates, Marilyn Monroe, Thelma Ritter\r\n', 'Drama. Stage Play. Cult Movie ');
