(188, 'Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//bJLJAtGjBj836UjJZNOwgrfe5Ps.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//vgvw6w1CtcFkuXXn004S5wQsHRl.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'After seven months have passed without a culprit in her daughter\'s murder case, Mildred Hayes makes a bold move, painting three signs leading into her town with a controversial message directed at Bill Willoughby, the town\'s revered chief of police. When his second-in-command Officer Jason Dixon, an immature mother\'s boy with a penchant for violence, gets involved, the battle between Mildred and Ebbing\'s law enforcement is only exacerbated.', 21, '2017-11-10', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jit3YhGx5pU', 8, 7559, 115, 'United Kingdom', 'Martin McDonagh', 'Martin McDonagh', 'Frances McDormand, Woody Harrelson, Sam Rockwell, John Hawkes, Peter Dinklage, Caleb Landry Jones, Lucas Hedges, Abbie Cornish, Brendan Sexton III, Samara Weaving, Kerry Condon, Nick Searcy, Lawrence Turner, Amanda Warren, Michael Aaron Milligan, William J. Harrison, Sandy Martin, Christopher Berry, Zeljko Ivanek, Alejandro Barrios, Darrell Britt-Gibson, Clarke Peters, Jason Ledford, Malaya Rivera Drew\r\n', 'Thriller. Drama. Comedy. Black Comedy. Racism. Sexual Abuse '),
(189, 'Lion', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//fgffluhvdOv79SkYaKrfRA0xkf4.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//kCELJH1tCmaRLqvwIgKDb09aEaw.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'A five-year-old Indian boy gets lost on the streets of Calcutta, thousands of kilometers from home. He survives many challenges before being adopted by a couple in Australia; 25 years later, he sets out to find his lost family.', 28, '2016-01-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/-RNI9o06vqo', 8, 5222, 118, 'Australia', 'Garth Davis', 'Luke Davies (Novel: Saroo Brierley)', 'Dev Patel, Sunny Pawar, Nicole Kidman, Rooney Mara, David Wenham, Nawazuddin Siddique, Tannishtha Chatterjee, Deepti Naval, Priyanka Bose, Divian Ladwa\r\n', 'Drama. Childhood. Poverty. Adoption. Trains. Based On A True Story '),
(190, 'On My Skin', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//lpuehRS74pgVYIQ6ZQ2fIAaoAvo.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//rwPgE6fLxuJmPWi8fFjgENJMAjr.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'it', 'The incredible true story behind the most controversial Italian court cases in recent years. Stefano Cucchi was arrested for a minor crime and mysteriously found dead during his detention. In one week\'s time, a family is changed forever.', 10, '2018-09-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/ep-O2Nl0P0s', 8, 1570, 100, 'Italy', 'Alessio Cremonini', 'Alessio Cremonini, Lisa Nur Sultan', 'Alessandro Borghi, Massimiliano Tortora, Milvia Marigliano, Jasmine Trinca, Walter Nestola, Mauro Conte, Paolo D Bovani, Emanuele Cerman, Andrea Ottavi, Andrea Lattanzi, Daniele Blando, Italo Amerighi, Gabriele Coppola, Mauro Mandolini\r\n', 'Drama. Based On A True Story. Prison Drama '),
(192, 'In the Mood for Love', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//n4GJFGzsc7NinI1VeGDXIcQjtU2.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//iYypPT4bhqXfq1b6EnmxvRt6b2Y.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'cn', 'A melancholy story set in Hong Kong in 1962. A woman and a man who live in the same crowded apartment building discover that their husband and wife are having an affair.', 17, '2000-09-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/bOq_jnvDXV8', 8, 1347, 99, 'Hong Kong', 'Wong Kar-Wai', 'Wong Kar-Wai', 'Tony Leung Chiu-Wai, Maggie Cheung, Rebecca Pan, Siu Ping-Lam, Mama Hung, Chan Man-Lei, Koo Kam-Wah, Yu Hsien, Chow Po-Chun, Joe Cheung, Kelly Lai\r\n', 'Romance. Drama. Romantic Drama. 1960s. Cult Movie '),
(193, 'M', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//czULBNVlzFFsCyXNTgllIvTPEgf.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//6hg2UClwHGnBojemFrLgiF1WK8A.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'de', 'In this classic German thriller, Hans Beckert, a serial killer who preys on children, becomes the focus of a massive Berlin police manhunt. Beckert\'s heinous crimes are so repellant and disruptive to city life that he is even targeted by others in the seedy underworld network. With both cops and criminals in pursuit, the murderer soon realizes that people are on his trail, sending him into a tense, panicked attempt to escape justice.', 14, '1931-05-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/nsVproWjN6c', 8, 1317, 117, 'Germany', 'Fritz Lang', 'Thea von Harbou, Fritz Lang', 'Peter Lorre, Otto Wernicke, Gustaf Gründgens, Theo Lingen, Theodor Loos, Georg John, Ellen Widman, Inge Landgut\r\n', 'Thriller. Mystery. Crime. Serial Killers. German Expressionism. Cult Movie '),
(194, 'The Red Shoes', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//cSbBSHHiy849SUhyTW6FX4Dbj43.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//7kUiA3FlSnZcsULjz1PhPZbo2gp.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'In this classic drama, Vicky Page is an aspiring ballerina torn between her dedication to dance and her desire to love. While her imperious instructor, Boris Lermontov, urges to her to forget anything but ballet, Vicky begins to fall for the charming young composer Julian Craster. Eventually Vicky, under great emotional stress, must choose to pursue either her art or her romance, a decision that carries serious consequences.', 10, '1948-07-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/xRV6LPtRUyc', 8, 357, 133, 'United Kingdom', 'Michael Powell, Emeric Pressburger\r\n', 'Emeric Pressburger', 'Anton Walbrook, Moira Shearer, Marius Goring, Leonid Massine, Albert Basserman, Robert Helpmann, Ludmilla Tcherina, Esmond Knight\r\n', 'Drama. Romance. Ballet. Melodrama '),
(195, 'The Tale of the Princess Kaguya', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//imUJOrtNf8EWameChpaRLXSaX4w.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//mWRQNlWXYYfd2z4FRm99MsgHgiA.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'ja', 'Found inside a shining stalk of bamboo by an old bamboo cutter and his wife, a tiny girl grows rapidly into an exquisite young lady. The mysterious young princess enthralls all who encounter her - but ultimately she must confront her fate, the punishment for her crime.', 13, '2013-11-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/W71mtorCZDw', 8, 1108, 137, 'Japan', 'Isao Takahata', 'Isao Takahata, Riko Sakaguchi', 'Animation', 'Animation. Fantasy. Drama. Fairy Tales / Fables. 9th Century '),
(196, 'The 400 Blows', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//rJ4PKIHYarZfVOqpSxcjRIvC1A9.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//12PuU23kkDLvTd0nb8hMlE3oShB.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'fr', 'For young Parisian boy Antoine Doinel, life is one difficult situation after another. Surrounded by inconsiderate adults, including his neglectful parents, Antoine spends his days with his best friend, Rene, trying to plan for a better life. When one of their schemes goes awry, Antoine ends up in trouble with the law, leading to even more conflicts with unsympathetic authority figures.', 12, '1959-06-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/i89oN8v7RdY', 8, 1328, 99, 'France', 'François Truffaut', 'Marcel Moussy, François Truffaut', 'Jean-Pierre Léaud, Claire Maurier, Albert Rémy, Guy Decomble, Georges Flamant, Patrick Auffay, Jeanne Moreau\r\n', 'Drama. Nouvelle vague (New Wave). Cult Movie. Teen/coming-of-age. Education '),
(197, 'Paris, Texas', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//pAKpSMrCv9HQdMKvIdLgTdpKh5f.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//riLA3cq2R8m6Rx1z6OpdE8PH8H9.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'A man wanders out of the desert not knowing who he is. His brother finds him, and helps to pull his memory back of the life he led before he walked out on his family and disappeared four years earlier.', 15, '1984-08-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/9e590FeeGCM', 8, 1030, 146, 'Germany - West Germany (FRG)', 'Wim Wenders', 'Sam Shepard', 'Harry Dean Stanton, Nastassja Kinski, Dean Stockwell, Aurore Clément, Hunter Carson, Bernhard Wicki, Socorro Valdez, John Lurie, Sally Norvell, Sharon Menzel, Tom Farrell, Viva\r\n', 'Drama. Road Movie. Cult Movie '),
(198, 'Django Unchained', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//s4cJQaj40SwMifUrrdtdOJsjnRO.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//4E4TTsCXVFyhBtYu9fKy0gIT3Ih.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'With the help of a German bounty hunter, a freed slave sets out to rescue his wife from a brutal Mississippi plantation owner.', 44, '2012-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/0fUCuvNlOCg', 8, 20197, 165, 'United States', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Jamie Foxx, Christoph Waltz, Leonardo DiCaprio, Kerry Washington, Samuel L. Jackson, Don Johnson, Walton Goggins, Laura Cayouette, Dennis Christopher, M.C. Gainey, James Remar, Michael Parks, Bruce Dern, James Parks, Cooper Huckabee, Doc Duhame, Franco Nero, Quentin Tarantino, James Russo, Jonah Hill, Dana Gourrier, Sammi Rotibi, Nichole Galicia, Ato Essandoh, David Steen, Amber Tamblyn, Zoe Bell, Russ Tamblyn, Tom Savini, Rex Linn, Lee Horsley, John Jarratt\r\n', 'Western. Southern Gothic. Slavery. Racism. Spaghetti Western. 19th Century. Revenge '),
(199, 'Alien', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//AmR3JG1VQVxU8TfAvljUhfSFUOx.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//vfrQk5IPloGg1v9Rzbh2Eg3VGyM.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'During its return to the earth, commercial spaceship Nostromo intercepts a distress signal from a distant planet. When a three-member team of the crew discovers a chamber containing thousands of eggs on the planet, a creature inside one of the eggs attacks an explorer. The entire crew is unaware of the impending nightmare set to descend upon them when the alien parasite planted inside its unfortunate host is birthed.', 52, '1979-05-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/LjLamj-b0I8', 8, 10173, 117, 'United States', 'Ridley Scott', 'Dan O\'Bannon (Story: Ronald Shusett)', 'Sigourney Weaver, John Hurt, Yaphet Kotto, Tom Skerritt, Veronica Cartwright, Harry Dean Stanton, Ian Holm\r\n', 'Sci-Fi. Horror. Aliens. Space Adventure. Cult Movie '),
(200, 'There Will Be Blood', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//xFuRZtuTbTY3S1QLY8Y9XYH1JCk.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w300//fa0RDkAlCec0STeMNAhPaF89q6U.jpg?api_key=73335406cba0f2d2b6be748d34df365b&language=en-US', 'en', 'Ruthless silver miner, turned oil prospector, Daniel Plainview, moves to oil-rich California. Using his son to project a trustworthy, family-man image, Plainview cons local landowners into selling him their valuable properties for a pittance. However, local preacher Eli Sunday suspects Plainview\'s motives and intentions, starting a slow-burning feud that threatens both their lives.', 19, '2007-12-28', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/FeSLPELpMeM', 8, 4422, 158, 'United States', 'Paul Thomas Anderson', 'Paul Thomas Anderson (Novel: Upton Sinclair)', 'Daniel Day-Lewis, Paul Dano, Kevin J. O\'Connor, Ciarán Hinds, Russell Harvard, Dillon Freasier, Sydney McCallister, David Willis, David Warshofsky, Colton Woodward, Colleen Foy\r\n', 'Drama. Historical. 1920s. Small Town Life (North-american) ');

